  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if Linezolid is safe for adult Filipino patients
      diagnosed with gram positive infections.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The subjects were identified after the physician decided to prescribed the drug to the
      subject.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
