Nosocomial infection, cSSTI: Linezolid for 600mg (IV or oral) every 12 hours for 10-14 days
Uncomplicated SSTI: Linezolid for 400mg oral every 12 hours for 10-14 days</description>
    <arm_group_label>Group 1</arm_group_label>
